      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in poor condition and is ideal for someone looking for a major project or a source for parts. The engine has significant issues, including a heavy knock and consistent overheating, and the transmission slips when shifting into higher gears. Externally, the body shows considerable rust on the rocker panels and several large dents, while the interior has significant tearing in the upholstery. It is currently not reliable for daily driving and will likely need to be towed from the lot.",
