      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary vehicle, maintained to the highest standards of automotive excellence. This unit remains in pristine showroom condition, exhibiting a flawless exterior and an interior that retains its original factory luster. Every mechanical component has been rigorously inspected to ensure peak performance, offering the discerning buyer a peerless driving experience. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a vehicle of such uncompromising pedigree and aesthetic perfection.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
