      "description": "Presented for your consideration is a vehicle of exceptional caliber, maintained to the highest standards of automotive excellence. This unit exhibits a showroom-grade aesthetic, coupled with flawless mechanical integrity. Every detail reflects a commitment to preservation, ensuring an acquisition that meets the most discerning expectations of quality and performance.",
      "price": 48500.0,
