    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b You have seriously got to see this absolute beauty! I\u2019ve taken such good care of her, and she\u2019s still looking and driving like she just rolled off the showroom floor. Not a scratch, not a dent\u2014just pure perfection! It\u2019s been my pride and joy, but it's time for someone else to enjoy that 'new car' feel without the brand-new price tag. It\u2019s super clean, super smooth, and ready for a new home. Come by and take a look, I promise you won't be disappointed! \ud83d\ude97\u2728",
      "price": 43900.0,
