    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting an uncompromising 2004 BMW M3 in a condition that satisfies the most rigorous technical inspection. At its heart lies the S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and high-pressure double-VANOS variable valve timing, delivering a razor-sharp 7,900 RPM redline. This chassis has been preserved with surgical precision, featuring a factory-straight body and a reinforced rear subframe to ensure structural rigidity. The Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox offers tactile, short-throw engagement, channeling power through a perfectly calibrated limited-slip differential. Mechanical maintenance is exhaustive, including proactive rod bearing replacement and a recent valve adjustment to ensure peak volumetric efficiency. From the pristine undercarriage to the taut suspension geometry, this vehicle remains a reference-standard example of Bavarian engineering.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 4
    },
